<taxonomicName box="[284,482,1918,1940]" class="Amphibia" family="Ranidae" genus="Rana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Anura" pageId="7" pageNumber="258" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="margaritifera">
<emphasis box="[284,482,1918,1940]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="258">Rana margaritifera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
figured in Seba (1734), plate 71, figures 6 and 7. (A) Black-and-white copy of the Missouri Botanical Garden, Saint Louis, Missouri (USA), available at &lt;http://www.animalbase.org&gt;. (B) Hand painted reprinted from the copy of the Koninklijke Bibliotheek, The Hague, Netherlands, by Taschen, Köln. (C) Hand painted copy of the Museu Nacional, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil.
</paragraph>
